OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FThames Water says          
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fturnaround will 'take time'
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Thames Water has said that reviving the
OL,6, business will "take time" as it        
OL,7, reported sliding profits and an        
OL,8, increase in its huge debt pile.        
OL,10,FProfits for the first half of its      
OL,11,Ffinancial year more than halved to     
OL,12,F#246m, while debts rose 7% to #14.7bn. 
OL,14,FThames Water secured extra funds in    
OL,15,FJuly, but questions have been raised   
OL,16,Fover the nature of the support.        
OL,18,FThe head of the Environment Committee  
OL,19,Fsaid he could recall the firm's boss to
OL,20,Fbe quizzed by MPs over the deal.       
